body: "## Agent need\nProject management = context management: an agent must retrieve existing context before acting, both to reuse knowledge and to avoid creating duplicate items.\n\n## Delivered surface (pm-ydp6)\nBM25 + corpus; vector-stores + embedding-batches; hybrid relevance; inline-field query parser + --highlight; background-refresh + staleness; pm eval golden-query harness.\n\n## Verified by\nsearch-bm25 tests and the golden-queries eval fixtures. Enduring agent-value statement for the search capability; new work lands in pm-ydp6."
